posting_body: ['Welcome home!', 'Schedule a Tour!', 'Book an appointment online at 2tour.site/OHD/NJQJ', 'Fountainhead Apartments offers a convenient location, moments from downtown Minneapolis and St. Paul, Mall of America, and the MSP Airport.', 'Fountainhead Apartments feature spacious one, two, and three-bedroom apartment homes, fiber-optic internet service is available, patios/balconies, fountains, an outdoor pool, fitness center, and many barbecue/picnic areas.', 'Fountainhead Apartments is on the bus line.', 'Visit today and see why you will love to call Fountainhead home!', 'Home Amenities', 'Fiber-optic internet service available', 'Wall air conditioning', 'Walk-in closet', 'Balcony or patio options', 'Window coverings', 'Appliances in kitchen', 'Ceiling fans', 'Community Amenities', '24 hour emergency maintenance', 'Pet friendly - some restrictions apply', 'Laundry facility', 'Fitness center', 'Outdoor swimming pool', 'Party room', 'Off street parking', 'Volleyball court', 'Playground', 'BBQ & picnic area', 'Car wash station', 'Fountainhead Apartments Information', 'Address:', '7617 Knox Ave S, Richfield MN, 55423', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Details/?pid=8', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Application Fee:', '$45', 'Pet Fee:', '$100 - 300 (Note: Varies By Number & Type Of Pet(s))', 'Pet Deposit:', '$200 - 400 (Note: Varies By Number Of Pets)', 'Office Hours', 'Monday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Tuesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Wednesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Thursday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Friday:', '9:00AM - 5:00PM', 'Saturday:', '11:00AM - 3:00PM', 'Sunday:', '12:00PM - 3:00PM']
